    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 factors. Twelve factors met or exceeded required levels. The discretization error factor achieved Gradation 2 against a required Gradation 3; the team judged the 8.3% GCI value sufficiently close to the 5% threshold and noted compensating confidence from the output comparison results. On balance, the team accepted the package at Medium assurance level. No further remediation was required prior to submission.",
